"`Flux<PartEvent>` returned from the `PartEventHttpMessageReader` instead of "
"using `@RequestPart`, as that implies `Map`-like access to individual parts "
"by name and, hence, requires parsing multipart data in full.  By contrast, "
"you can use `@RequestBody` to decode the content to `Flux<PartEvent>` "
"without collecting to a `MultiValueMap`."
msgstr ""

