#: /mnt/c/Users/etrees/Desktop/private/spring-framework/origin/framework-docs/modules/ROOT/pages/web/webflux/reactive-spring.adoc:732
msgid ""
"Applications can register custom codecs for supporting additional media "
"types, or specific behaviors that are not supported by the default codecs."
