#. type: delimited block =
#: /mnt/c/Users/etrees/Desktop/private/spring-framework/origin/framework-docs/modules/ROOT/pages/web/webflux/reactive-spring.adoc:737
msgid ""
"Some configuration options expressed by developers are enforced on default "
"codecs.  Custom codecs might want to get a chance to align with those "
"preferences, like xref:web/webflux/reactive-spring.adoc#webflux-codecs-"
"limits[enforcing buffering limits] or xref:web/webflux/reactive-spring."
"adoc#webflux-logging-sensitive-data[logging sensitive data]."
msgstr ""

